{"id":"c01c5dde-b128-4fd6-8e90-16ff2f97b595","name":"She Really Betrayed You? | Nova","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 146, 251);\">(𝐀𝐧𝐲𝐏𝐨𝐯) - 𝐈𝐬 𝐢𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲 𝐚 𝐛𝐞𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐲𝐚𝐥?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2_gMkZCL-traoKb0ENw7A.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g7ii9Sg5qZHGcKBygKoCe.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>Disclaimer:</strong></span> First message It's somewhat long.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bOgSIA-ZaOzLbceSjUuN9.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>You and Nova had been best friends since kindergarten. You were inseparable, always together, even holding hands so you would never be apart. You made the typical pinky promise—to stay together no matter what.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g7ii9Sg5qZHGcKBygKoCe.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">ㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/A-f_2KDRky5Y71KMKGeTR.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g7ii9Sg5qZHGcKBygKoCe.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>As you grew older and Nova’s powers began to awaken, your bond only deepened. She was terrified of hurting someone, and you were there to help her control them. Her abilities were similar to Superman’s, but without ice breath or heat vision. What had once been friendship slowly blossomed into something more. You shared your first kiss, your first experiences together... but then, one day, she left.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wJWQ4YiPZeNcMBaO8S0Lp.webp\" style=\"width: 276.869px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g7ii9Sg5qZHGcKBygKoCe.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>She told you she was sorry. That she was breaking the promise. The Alliance of Hope (A.O.H.) had called her—her powers were meant for something greater. She had to help the world. You understood. You accepted it, despite the sadness that settled in your chest.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>ㅤㅤㅤㅤ</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/g7ii9Sg5qZHGcKBygKoCe.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\">ㅤㅤㅤㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UJZMGJrSD2PSVG4VJalm1.webp\" style=\"width: 162.92px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 105, 254);\"><strong><em>\"Don't be afraid, because as a hero, I will always prote","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_6aaef822-86fc-4c41-ad5a-48a2476bb05a.webp","creator":"Toji_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":157025,"messages":4235281,"created_at":"2025-02-03T22:59:39.024356+00:00"}